
# Xero Voiceassistat

A simple voice assistant, equipped with a webserver for controling the raspberry pi remotly. It can do a few things including playing music, and setting an alarm. It structured and easily expandable. 




## Features

-  Get the time
-  Get the date
-  Stop Playing music
-  Radio player
-  Play Music via Youtube
-  Search in Wikipedia
-  Set an Alarm


## TODO

-  GPT support for questions that are outside the predefined parameters
